474
01:04:09,880 --> 01:04:12,160
 prouzrokovati različite reakcije,

475
01:04:12,160 --> 01:04:13,880
 čak i one agresive, čak i one negativne.

476
01:04:13,880 --> 01:04:16,640
 Evo, spomenuli smo u ovom podcastu

477
01:04:16,640 --> 01:04:17,620
