493
01:04:49,280 --> 01:04:50,940
 onda to je jedna velika moć

494
01:04:50,940 --> 01:04:52,560
 koja, dakle,

495
01:04:52,560 --> 01:04:54,580
 kreše krila sotoni.

496
01:04:54,580 --> 01:04:55,740
 Tako da nije ni čudo

497
01:04:55,740 --> 01:04:57,680
